<li><i>Total Eclipse</i> (August 1999)&#160;– the main presenter on the historic solar Eclipse in Cornwall on <a href="/wiki/BBC_One" title="BBC One">BBC One</a>.</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/2000_Today" title="2000 Today">2000 Today</a></i> – Co-presenter</li>
