<li><i>Inside the National Trust</i> (2013) – Presenter</li>
<li><i>Britain's Secret Homes</i> (2013) – Co-presenter</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/I%27m_a_Celebrity...Get_Me_Out_of_Here!_(UK_TV_series)" title="I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! (UK TV series)">I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here!</a></i> (2014) – Contestant</li>
<li><i>Pompeii with Michael Buerk</i> (2016) – Presenter</li>
<li><i>Royal Recipes</i> (2017) – Presenter</li>
